Coral Diagnostic PRPQ NOTES:

- dgemm test
  dgemm Diag test invokes Spectrum mpi script: 
     /opt/ibm/spectrum_mpi/healthcheck/dgemm/run.dgemm
  Please read /opt/ibm/spectrum_mpi/healthcheck/dgemm/README.dgemm file and 
  make the necessary modifications.

- dgemm-gpu test
  dgemm-gpu Diag test invokes Spectrum mpi script: 
     /opt/ibm/spectrum_mpi/healthcheck/dgemm/run.dgemm_gpu
  Please read /opt/ibm/spectrum_mpi/healthcheck/dgemm_gpu/README.dgemm_gpu file  
  and make the necessary modifications.


- fieldiag test
  fieldiag Diag test invokes NVIDIA fieldiag test. Currently it does not 
  support Volta. The test will FAIL.
  
